to 10 million but in 1986 the companys backer arizona refining 
was sold and quit bonding savala asphalt and construction 
enterprises inc 
mrs savala said her companys revenues plummeted to 1 million 
leaving the savalas with big bills to pay 
her story was one of several told by witnesses before the 
