on a leather strap around the young womans neck 
hung a plumsized chunk of quartz 
it puts a circle of power around you that keeps you feeling 
protected said marybeth stroebel of jersey city n j a graphic 
artist for a manhattan advertising firm 
the crystal shields you she said if you know how to get 
in tune with it it helps you be more safe and calm when you 
