<TEXT>
traffic droned on the new jersey turnpike 
just as on any other tuesday morning commuters passed through the 
rest area here just as sleepyeyed but something was amiss and if 
robert cieplensky hadnt spotted it someone might be dead now in 
new york perhaps or washington or toronto from the shrapnel of a 
homemade bomb 
