nonetheless jenkins said the united states generally lacks the 
driving forces of homegrown terrorism ideology usually 
americans kill in personal quarrels not for causes and ethnic 
grievances the independence movement in puerto rico is an 
exception 
as for foreign terrorists why attack on american soil when there 
are convenient us targets abroad from embassies to fastfood 
restaurants its easier to cross a street than cross an ocean to 
